<body>
<main class="home">
	<div class="container">	
		<h1>Alex J. Gustafson Fitness</h1>

		<h2>Starting Strength in Louisville, KY</h2>
		<p>Alex owns and coaches <a href="https://www.gus.coach">Gus's Barbell Club</a> in Louisville, KY. Gus's Barbell Club trains with the Starting Strength methodology.</p>

		<h2>CrossFit Training in Louisville, KY</h2>
		<div class="grid">
			<div>
				<p>Alex is a CrossFit Level 1 Trainer in Louisville, KY. He is a member at <a href="https://www.crossfitgoldenwarrior.com">CrossFit Golden Warrior</a>, a CrossFit affiliate gym in Shepherdsville, KY.</p>
				<p>Alex does not coach at any CrossFit affiliate nor does he operate his own CrossFit affiliate and thus does not sell any CrossFit services.</p>
			</div>
			<article class="trainer-directory-callout">
				<h3>Use the CrossFit Trainer Directory</h3>
				<p>Find Alex or another CrossFit trainer in Louisville, KY on the <a href="https://trainerdirectory.crossfit.com/results?lastname=gustafson&city=louisville&state=ky">CrossFit.com Trainer Directory.</a></p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="container">
		<h2>Education</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>CrossFit Level 1 Trainer</li>
			<li>CrossFit Judges Certificate (2022-23)</li>
			<li>CrossFit Lesson Planning Certificate</li>
			<li>CrossFit Programming Certificate</li>
			<li>CrossFit Scaling Certificate</li>
			<li>CrossFit Spot the Flaw Certificate</li>
			<li>American Red Cross Adult and Pediatric First Aid/CPR/AED</li>
			<li>OptimizeMe Nutrition | Nutrition Essentials Masterclass (Spring 2022)</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Social Media</h2>
		<p>Instagram: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/alexjgustafson/">@alexjgustafson</a></p>

	</div>

	<div class="contact">		
		<div class="container compact">			
			<h2 class="centered">Get in Touch</h2>
			<form name="fitness-contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true">
				<p>
					<label>Your Name: <input type="text" name="name" /></label>   
				</p>
				<p>
					<label>Your Email: <input type="email" name="email" /></label>
				</p>
				<p>
					<label>Message: <textarea name="message"></textarea></label>
				</p>
				<p>
					<button type="submit">Send</button>
				</p>
			</form>
		</div>
	</div>
</main>
